<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hospital Home Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #4b0082;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        header .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header .logo img {
            height: 70px; /* Default size, keeping the header's height intact */
            width: 100px; /* Default size, keeping the header's height intact */
            margin-right: 15px;
        }

        header nav {
            display: flex;
        }

        header nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        header nav a:hover {
            color: #dda0dd;
        }

        .hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #e6e6fa;
        }

        .hero .content {
            max-width: 50%;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #4b0082;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        

        

        .hero img {
            width: 60%; /* Adjust size to fit the layout */
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #4b0082;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .hero .content, .hero img {
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            header nav {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            header nav a {
                margin: 5px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/images/Care_Connect-removebg-preview.png" alt="Hospital Logo">
            <h1>Care Connect</h1>
        </div>
        <nav>
           
            <a href="/index">Services</a>
            <a href="#doctors">Doctors</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Trusted, Proven, Award-Winning Care</h1>
            <p>Our mission is to offer world-class healthcare services with a compassionate approach, 
                ensuring that every patient receives the attention and care they need to regain their 
                health and independence. We work closely with medical professionals,
                 caregivers, and families to create a healing environment where patients can thrive.</p>
            
        </div>
        <img src="/images/doctor.jpg" alt="Doctor and Patient">
    </section>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2024 Care Connect. All rights reserved. | Emergency Contact: +123-456-7890
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
